{"tid":583354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工聯會鄧家彪今直播譴責九巴解僱葉蔚琳　再刪片","createTime":"2018-03-07T02:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T07:01:57.000Z","uid":6604,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a29bffdf06ffd358765021167c4ff5f9226b17a1","tid":583354,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E6%9B%BE%E5%98%B2%E7%BD%B7%E9%A7%9B-%E7%99%BD%E7%97%B4-%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E9%84%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BD%AA%E4%BB%8A%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E8%91%89%E8%94%9A%E7%90%B3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2598%25B2%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%2597%25B4-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2584%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BD%25AA%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E8%2591%2589%25E8%2594%259A%25E7%2590%25B3%2F&d=ZFb6EgCh8lAR4UKiz3kEXf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2aa1e0ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2597%2597%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%2598%25B2%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E9%25A7%259B-%25E7%2599%25BD%25E7%2597%25B4-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2584%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BD%25AA%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2583%25B1%25E8%2591%2589%25E8%2594%259A%25E7%2590%25B3%2F&h=a4e313e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%97%97%E4%B8%8B%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E6%9B%BE%E5%98%B2%E7%BD%B7%E9%A7%9B-%E7%99%BD%E7%97%B4-%E5%B7%A5%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E9%84%A7%E5%AE%B6%E5%BD%AA%E4%BB%8A%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4%E8%A7%A3%E5%83%B1%E8%91%89%E8%94%9A%E7%90%B3/</a><br />\n<br />\n工聯會屬下的九巴工會，一直反對罷駛行動。不過在「月薪車長大聯盟」發起人葉蔚琳被解僱後，工聯會議員陸頌雄及參選新界東補選的鄧家彪隨即發布影片，強烈抗議九巴的做法，並要求勞工處介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n不過影片惹來不少留言批評，有網民認為葉蔚琳被解僱是自作自受，甚至警告鄧家彪小心311補選選情。有關影片隨即被刪去。<br />\n<br />\n陸頌雄在影片中形容，九巴是「涉嫌不合法、不合理」解僱葉蔚琳。工聯會認為九巴的做法絕對不能接受，並予以強烈譴責。他指巴士公司的做法，是有打壓員工爭取合理權利之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n鄧家彪亦指，強烈譴責九巴涉嫌不合法、不合理解僱車長，指根據法例及《基本法》，打工仔有權發起工業行動。他質疑解僱的決定是視法律如無物，呼籲勞工處主動介入調查，若證據充份應作出起訴。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會屬下的「汽車交通運輸業總工會九巴分會」，早前被指私下與資方達成薪酬方案，葉蔚琳亦曾直指九巴分會是出賣員工。九巴分會副主任黎兆聰早前稱自己是理性工會，「唔會學啲白痴咁，按章工作、一人罷工」。<br />\n<br />\n鄧家彪是立法會補選新界東的候選人，其他同區候選人包括范國威、黃成智、方國珊、陳玉娥、趙佩玉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日要炒熱呢單新聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfa3de8b7af10dd407d41a6d52bb552d2370d4f","tid":583354,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:18:05.000Z","msg":"借&quot;搵岑麗香口膠&quot;巴打圖一貼<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/26/203310_0b08d0a1f05ceec31d5fe46e94844d4f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F26%2F203310_0b08d0a1f05ceec31d5fe46e94844d4f.png&h=f99586d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15a81003858da3b7f691673a82ed7c3e22b6590b","tid":583354,"uid":44358,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:25:31.000Z","msg":"連自己主要服務既勞工，都可以出賣。<br />\n<br />\n比呢班工賊會當選，肯肯定加倍賣港，大家準備食屎都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9c4a3695377bc372a21b763afe7acdccec731a","tid":583354,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T02:30:13.000Z","msg":"冇事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e35dfe21a2177adf80179561240aa37b9c14a7